text: The Federal Service for State Registration, Cadastre and Cartography (Rosreestr; ) is the Russian federal agency of geodesy, cartography and real estate. It was established in 2008 in Moscow after the closure of the previous organization that was established during the Soviet period. == Other websites == * The Federal Service for State Registration, Cadastre and Cartography Category:Moscow Category:National mapping agencies Category:2008 establishments in Asia
